                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Environment Variables</h3>
                        <p class="mt-1 text-neutral-400">Store secret keys in .env files, not hard-coded into the application.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="phase-card p-6 rounded-xl flex items-start space-x-4">
