                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">JWT Best Practices</h3>
                        <p class="mt-1 text-neutral-400">Use short expiration times for tokens and manage refresh tokens securely.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                 <div class="phase-card p-6 rounded-xl flex items-start space-x-4">
                    <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-rose-400 flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9l4-4 4 4m0 6l-4 4-4-4"></path></svg>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Role-Based Access</h3>
                        <p class="mt-1 text-neutral-400">Implement controls so only admin users can access sensitive backend APIs.</p>
